query: What are the top leaderboard scores in the Kaggle Santa 2025 Christmas Tree Packing competition and what techniques did winners use?

results.title: ANSWER
results.text: The top leaderboard scores in the Kaggle Santa 2025 Christmas Tree Packing competition are approximately 68.89, 68.90, and 68.92, achieved by teams such as Jingle bins, sh, and KiRaRe ([Kaggle leaderboard](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/santa-2025/leaderboard), as of January 25, 2026). The winners primarily used advanced optimization techniques, including custom algorithms and model ensembling, to maximize packing efficiency ([Kaggle discussion](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/santa-2025/discussion/666880), as of January 9, 2026).
